  "title": "Construction Equipment & Operations Coordinator (West)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Support daily operations of workshop and store, ensuring compliance with safety regulations and company standards.</li>\n  <li>Manage issuance, return, and condition of tools, equipment, and materials to avoid delays in operations.</li>\n  <li>Track inventory levels of tools, spare parts, and consumables, ensuring proper storage and handling.</li>\n  <li>Generate and submit regular reports on stock, repairs, and equipment status to management.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with the project team to meet project-specific requirements and timelines.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>WSQ WSH certification or equivalent safety qualifications.</li>\n  <li>At least 2 years’ experience <strong>coordinating</strong> <strong>construction operations.</strong></li>\n  <li>Knowledge of construction equipment, tools, and maintenance procedures.</li>\n  <li>Ability to work independently, prioritize tasks, and coordinate effectively across teams.</li>\n  <li>Basic computer skills for inventory management and reporting.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
